'''Steam''' software-distributseplatförm die emaakt is deur [[Valve Corporation]] en is veural bedoeld veur [[Computerspöl|computerspöllen]]. Op [[12 september]] [[2003]] wier de eerste värsie uut ebracht met allenig as bedoeling um updates veur [[Counter-Strike]] makkelijker te mäken en te verspreiden.<ref>[https://store.steampowered.com/news/183/ Steam Client Released]. Valve Corporation (12 september 2003). </ref><ref>[https://www.valvesoftware.com/nl/ About Valve]. Valve Corporation.</ref> In [[2018]] had Steam al 90 miljoen maondelikse gebrukers die vaeke online waren. In [[januari]] [[2019]] kwamp het 30.000 spöl op Steam.<ref>[https://steamcommunity.com/groups/steamworks/announcements/detail/1697194621363928453 Steam - 2018 Year in Review]. Steam (14 januari 2019).</ref><ref>[https://www.shacknews.com/article/109349/steam-now-has-30000-games-on-its-storefront Steam now has 30,000 games on its storefront]. Shacknews (14 januari 2019).</ref>

De eerste värsie van Steam wier allenig uut ebracht veur [[Windows]].

